      </td>
      <td>
        <p><b>Material cost (in sc)</b></p>
      </td>
      <td>
        <p><b>Description</b></p>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>
        <p>Common</p>
      </td>
      <td>
        <p>10</p>
      </td>
      <td>
        <p>200-500</p>
      </td>
      <td>
        <p>
          Items that hold minor powers, such as those you would find in a
          cantrip, chant, or prayer.
        </p>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>
        <p>Uncommon</p>
